Articles.Content:
This is normal behavior in the stock game. If you look in Squad/Resources/ResourceDefaults.cfg you'll see:

    RESOURCE_CONFIGURATION{	HeatEnabled = True			//Thermal effects for generators and drills	ECMinScale = 100			//Do not calc scaled EC till this warp	OverlayStyle = 1			//(Integer) 1=Line, 2=Dot, 3=Solid}

So warp over 100 and it just ignores EC. You can increase that value there and it'll carry across to everything in the game. Not sure if that's changeable via MM, but I wouldn't be surprised. MM is wizardry.
